    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-05-12T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-05-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="1299"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1299">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.1052/70</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Price</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-05-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 12, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your May 12. You will immediately inform the Government of Panama that this
                    Government expects immediate compliance with its demand for the complete
                    disarmament of police in Colon and Panama of high-powered rifles.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
